snippet.title: Sole Iron Tail: Short Game Teaser
snippet.description:
Get a glimpse at the cute independent game of Sole Iron Tail through this gameplay teaser!

Sole Iron Tail is a momentum-based platformer inspired by classic games like Sonic, based around sliding and charging with your tail through a multitude of levels as fast as your can!

Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/SoleIronTail
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1252190/Sole_Iron_Tail/
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/MhBpJR
